event.title: How to Overcome the Academic Stress
event.description: Hi, this Arthur Micheal. I am a studet counselor and I have been working for the education department for the last 8 years. I am organizing an event on 17th April regarding the most common issues faced by students in schools and colleges. The event includes different activities like career counseling, college life survival hacks, best essay writing service reviews and many more. Students and parents are humbly welcome.
